title: Answering Intimate Fan Questions About Our Personal Lives
description:
This week, Tasia and Camo sit down and answer fan questions. The two discuss what it's like pursuing a career their parents don't understand, their thoughts on Christianity and the afterlife, and whether or not they ever get in fights with each other. Tasia opens up about how going to jail helped shift her life in a better direction and what influenced her decision to name her daughter Greenly. Camo also reveals whether she sees kids in her future and so much more! Tune in for all the answers!!
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
